# SYNDICATE AI — Trivy CVE Ignore List
# Format: CVE-XXXX-XXXXX  # reason
#
# This file documents accepted risks. Every entry requires a justification.
# Review quarterly and remove entries when patches become available.
#
# Policy: Only suppress CVEs that are:
#   1. Unfixable (no upstream patch exists), OR
#   2. Not exploitable in our runtime context (no attack surface)
